videos.description: Ebuka Izundu blocks it on one end then gets it tossed to him on the other end for the flush, putting Miami up 39-34.
videos.headline: Izundu slams it following big block

videos.description: Devon Daniels aggressively rejects a shot under the rim with 35 seconds left to keep Miami from cutting into NC State's lead.
videos.headline: Daniels gets important block in final seconds
